Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Modern weddings
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bs1h
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 7 May 1978
Comparing two modern weddings to discover why it's best not to write your own order of service. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less